setEnabled

public void setEnabled(boolean enabled)
Turn on or off the graphers in this StatPage and add a DefColorFadeController to our StatQuad surfaces to fade them in or out

Parameters:
enabled - true to fade in and enable the contents of this stat page, false to fade them out and disable them.

addGraphSurfaces

public void addGraphSurfaces(StatQuad surface)
Setup and add a new graphing surface to this StatPage. Sets the CullHint to Always and the alpha to 0 in preparation for fadein.

Parameters:
